#MaskSeries : Naga Besukih

Naga Besuki is a mythical creature originating and believed by the people of Bali. 

The story of the dragon Besukih also appears in the legend of the creation of the Bali Strait. And it is said that the dragon besukih resides under the crater of Mount Agung.

This dragon is said to be very powerful. The scales of this dragon can fall off and turn into gold and diamonds.
